	* file/variables.cpp: fixed FC_SET* commands.

2007-10-24
	* model rendering updated.
	* optimised svg icons (partial).

2007-10-23
	* model/selection.cpp: fixed atom shift routines.
	* Qt: added atom shift functions. fixed zoomout hotkey.
	fixed crash on prevframe action. updated disorder stack page.
	* atom numbering in canvas and atomlist now 0->(N-1).

2007-10-21
	* templates/command.h: added 'string-as-is' variable specifier.
	* file/parse.h: fixed get_next_delim().
	* added Cambridge Database 'cds' filter.
	* classes/atom.h: removed atom colour reference.
	indexed colours now looked up in render subsystem.

2007-10-20
	* templates/command.h, base/sysfunc.h|cpp, file/parse.h|cpp: added expression evaluation.

